  <brief_title>Multi-resistant Enterobacteriaceae Colonisation in Less Than 32 Weeks Pregnant Women Admitted to the Hospital.</brief_title>
  <acronym>EME</acronym>
  <official_title>Multi-resistant Enterobacteriaceae Colonisation in Less Than 32 Weeks Pregnant Women Admitted in the Hospital: a Multicenter Study (EME Study).</official_title>
